22.  Qualifications. The Web, Multimedia and IT Consultant must possess: 

(i)  at least eight years of experience in the design and development of websites and 
multimedia products; 
(ii)  demonstrated experience creating social media networks and online surveys and 
editing electronic materials;  
(iii)  excellent  abilities  in  the  use  of  ICTs,  including  using  up-to-date  web-based 
resources; 
(iv)  good  working  knowledge  and  understanding  of  ADB’s  multimedia  products, 
websites and IT operations and its Department of External Relations is preferred; 
(v)  good interpersonal skills and experience working in a multicultural environment; 
and 
(vi)  good oral and written communication skills in English.
